      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ON THE RIVER (7) used the rails draw to advantage to get home last time at Horsham over 410m (23.18) after leading through, scoring by 2.75 lengths. Expected to go close again. THERMAL HEAT (2) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 0.7 lengths at this track in a handy 22.14. Fair draw can see a good run and goes well at this distance. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. One of main contenders. PROCYON (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Warrnambool behind Spring Laver (22.34) in a Mix 6/7. Has the early speed to give a sight. Expected to feature again. POETIC STAR (3) returns here with a good chance to improve on last time.",
